=== Phrase ===
'''[[курица#Russian|курам]] [[на]] [[смех]]''' (kúram násmekh)

# Something [[ridiculous]], silly, or completely [[unsatisfactory]]. (''Literally'' ‘for [[hen]]s to laugh’). 
#: Это же курам на смех! — ''That would be [[enough to make a cat laugh]]!''
#: Работа сделана курам на смех. — ''The job is done ridiculously [[wrong]].''

